'''強烈熱帶氣旋哈米甚'''（{{lang-en|Severe Tropical Cyclone Hamish}}）是一個於2009年3月對[[昆士蘭州|昆士蘭州]]及昆士蘭州外的[[珊瑚海|珊瑚海]][[大堡礁|大堡礁]]造成廣泛破壞的超強[[熱帶氣旋|氣旋]]，也是[[2008－2009年澳洲地區熱帶氣旋季|2008－2009年澳洲地區熱帶氣旋季]]（2008–09 Australian region cyclone season）的第8個獲{{tsl|en|Tropical cyclone naming|風暴命名|命名風暴}}。哈米甚在3月4日於接近[[约克角半岛|约克角半岛]]附近的一個[[低气压|低压區]]形成，翌日氣旋急速發展，成為[[熱帶氣旋等級|澳洲熱帶氣旋等級]]的一級氣旋。氣旋[[風眼|風眼]]於3月6日開始形成，氣旋等級進一步升至三級。同日深層[[大氣對流|對流]]包圍風眼，哈米甚的風力再次增強，於3月7日傍晚增強至五級氣旋。哈米甚於3月8日繼續向東南方向移動，不久後最接近陸地。氣旋在3月11日減弱並轉向西北方向移動，不久之後減弱為殘餘低氣壓，最終於3月14日消散。

==氣象歷史==
{{Storm path|Hamish 2009 track.png}}
2009年3月4日，氣旋在{{tsl|en|Lockhart River, Queensland|洛克哈特河 (昆士蘭)|洛克哈特河}}以東的[[珊瑚海|珊瑚海]]上空形成<ref name="TCR"/>。氣旋逐漸向西邊漂移，並於之後發展出[[大氣對流|對流]][[雨带|雨带]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite web|publisher=Bureau of Meteorology|year=2010|accessdate=2010-08-11|title=Severe Tropical Cyclone Hamish|url=http://www.bom.gov.au/announcements/sevwx/qld/qldtc20090304.shtml|archive-date=2011-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316143206/http://www.bom.gov.au/announcements/sevwx/qld/qldtc20090304.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。哈米甚正處於海溫較高的環境中，受惠於[[風切變|風切變]]弱及高空輻散良好的大氣條件而迅速增強<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2010-03-04 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Significant Tropical Weather Outlook |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ab/abpw10.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f25Pyy9L?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ab/abpw10.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-04  }}</ref>。翌日，氣旋頂部產生[[反氣旋|反氣旋]]令[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]流出，此時系統的對流開始沿其中心環繞，[[聯合颱風警報中心|聯合颱風警報中心]]在同一時間發出[[熱帶氣旋形成警報|熱帶氣旋形成警報]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-05 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone Formation Alert |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps21.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f2r4iwGi?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps21.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-05  }}</ref>。數小時後，澳洲氣象局將本低氣壓命名為熱帶氣旋哈米甚<ref name="TCR"/>。氣旋其後向南移動，面向位於東面的中層脊向南下行<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-05 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory One |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f3Tk2pQv?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-05  }}</ref>。不久後，聯合颱風警報中心開始對其進行熱帶風暴程度監測<ref name="JTWCBT">{{cite web|author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center|publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command|year=2010|accessdate=2010-08-11|title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Best Track|url=http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2009/2009s-bsh/bsh182009.txt|format=[[文本文件|TXT]]|archive-date=2010-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820114203/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/best_tracks/2009/2009s-bsh/bsh182009.txt|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

哈米甚被評定為熱帶氣旋之後不久，哈米甚開始[[快速增强|快速增强]]，並急速強化成為強烈熱帶氣旋，氣旋在3月6日的風速高達{{convert|120|km/h}}<ref name="TCR"/>。深層對流持續在一個清晰的低氣壓中心周圍發展，哈米甚的威力進一步加強<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Two |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f3wEwwSR?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。此外，衛星圖像顯示，[[風眼|風眼]]已經開始在風暴內部形成。受澳洲東部的[[高壓脊|高壓脊]]和中部的[[低壓槽|低壓槽]]限制，氣旋無法西移動，使氣旋開始朝東南方穩定行進<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Severe Tropical Cyclone Hamish Technical Bulletin- 1200 UTC 6 March 2009 |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f4b8xekw?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |archivedate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。根據3月7日的雷達觀測，哈米甚的風眼直徑約{{convert|28|km|mi|abbr=off}}<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2010-03-07 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Four |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f5cJdsB5?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-07}}</ref>。不久之後，氣旋進一步加強為[[熱帶氣旋等級|澳洲強度等級]]的5級氣旋，乃自2007年[[2006－2007年澳洲地區熱帶氣旋季#強烈熱帶氣旋喬治（George）|熱帶氣旋喬治]]以來首見。當天稍晚，熱帶氣旋哈米甚已達頂峰強度，風速高達{{convert|215|km/h}}，觀測到中心最低氣壓約為924[[帕斯卡|百帕]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.29[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）氣壓<ref name="TCR"/><ref>{{cite web|publisher=Bureau of Meteorology|date=2011-12-07|accessdate=2011-12-10|title=Database of Past Australian Tropical Cyclone Tracks|url=http://www.bom.gov.au/clim_data/IDCKMSTM0S.csv|format=[[逗号分隔值|.CSV]]|archive-date=2012-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227180359/http://www.bom.gov.au/clim_data/IDCKMSTM0S.csv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。聯合颱風警報中心所評估的中心最高持續風速相當於[[薩菲爾-辛普森颶風風力等級|薩菲爾-辛普森颶風風力等級]]中的五級颶風，一分鐘的持續風速峰值估計約為{{convert|250|km/h}}<ref name="JTWCBT"/>。

[[File:Severe_Tropical_Cyclone_Hamish_-_8_March_2009_(MODIS_Terra).jpg|thumb]]

哈米甚在巔峰的時期依然是小型的氣旋<ref>{{cite web|author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center|publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command|year=2010|accessdate=2010-08-12|title=Frequently Asked Questions: What is the average size of a tropical cyclone?|url=http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1#tcsize|archive-date=2013-07-08|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hxl4NuH6?url=http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/frequently-asked-questions-1#tcsize|dead-url=no}}</ref>，氣旋七級風暴風圈約為{{convert|440|km|mi|abbr=off}}，而其{{tsl|en|radius of outermost closed isobar|閉合等壓線}}半徑約為{{convert|260|km|mi|abbr=off}}<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-07 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Severe Tropical Cyclone Hamish Technical Bulletin 1800UTC 7 March 2009 |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f6dPEXab?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |archivedate=2009-03-07  }}</ref>。哈米甚維持了大約24小時的5級氣旋等级後<ref name="TCR"/>，因風切變在澳洲沿海地區的增加，哈米甚開始減弱<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-08 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Six |url=http://www.geocities.com/rattleman123456/001335-wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fB4QVVLl?url=http://www.geocities.com/rattleman123456/001335-wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-10  }}</ref>。3月8日下午，哈米甚進入[[眼牆置換循環|眼壁更替週期]]<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-08 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Severe Tropical Cyclone Hamish Technical Bulletin 1200UTC 8 March 2009 |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f7pdEtV7?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |archivedate=2009-03-08  }}</ref>，以致它在其後幾天一直維持四級氣旋之強度<ref name="TCR"/>。由於從澳洲西部而來的低壓槽逼近，[[風切變|風切變]]持續增加，哈米甚在3月10日出現穩定減弱的跡象<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-10 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Ten |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fAO3yCaM?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-10  }}</ref>。翌日，哈米甚受到西側與南側的氣流，與東北側弱高壓脊所形成的西北側導引氣流相互影響下，以致於哈米甚的移動速度減慢<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2009-03-11 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Twelve |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fBalVjaN?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-11  }}</ref>，哈米甚因而在3月11日減弱至強烈熱帶氣旋強度以下<ref name="TCR"/>。

在3月11日整天，哈米甚的中心上空已無對流重新發展，聯合颱風警報中心發出關於哈米甚的最後一次警報<ref>{{cite web |author=Joint Typhoon Warning Center |publisher=Naval Meteorology and Oceanography Command |date=2010-03-11 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone 18P (Hamish) Advisory Fourteen (Final) |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fD9kzWV4?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/wt/wtps31.pgtw..txt |archivedate=2009-03-12  }}</ref>。澳洲氣象局在大約同一時間評定並宣布哈米甚已減弱成為[[後熱帶氣旋|殘餘低氣壓]]；然而氣旋受其南部的高壓脊影響，轉至趨向西北方向，氣象局仍繼續監測其殘餘低氣壓<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-11 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Tropical Cyclone Hamish Technical Bulletin 0600UTC 11 March 2009 |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fBoKg0Ec?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |archivedate=2009-03-11  }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-11 |accessdate=2010-08-11 |title=Ex-Tropical Cyclone Hamish Technical Bulletin 1200UTC 11 March 2009 (Final) |url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fCRPSGvZ?url=http://weather.noaa.gov/pub/data/raw/ax/axau21.abrf..txt |archivedate=2009-03-11  }}</ref>。哈米甚的殘餘系統於其後數天以不穩定的路径向西北折返，最終於3月14日消散<ref name="JTWCBT"/>。哈米甚亦從未在澳洲陸地區域登陸<ref name="JTWCBT"/>。

==防災準備措施==
[[File:Severe_Tropical_Cyclone_Hamish_-_9_March_2009_(MODIS_Aqua).jpg|thumb]]沿海一帶出沒]]

哈米甚在3月4日形成[[熱帶低氣壓|熱帶低氣壓]]後，澳洲當局向昆士蘭州{{tsl|en|Cape Melville|梅爾維爾角 (昆士蘭州)|梅爾維爾角}}與{{tsl|en|Bowen, Queensland|寶雲 (昆士蘭州)|寶雲}}之間的區域發出對哈米甚的氣旋警報<ref name="TCA1">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-05 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 1 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f2pKFbUn?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-05  }}</ref>。翌日接近清晨時，當局又向由梅爾維爾角至{{tsl|en|Cardwell, Queensland|卡德威爾 (昆士蘭州)|卡德威爾}}之間的區域發出氣旋警報，氣旋警報的範圍也擴展至[[海曼島|海曼島]]<ref name="TCA3">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 3 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f3TWluwJ?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-05  }}</ref>，之後更擴展至[[麥凱_(昆士蘭州)|麥凱]]及{{tsl|en|St Lawrence, Queensland|聖勞倫斯 (昆士蘭州)|聖勞倫斯}}<ref name="TCA4">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 4 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f3drB705?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-05  }}</ref><ref name="TCA5">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 5 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f3v65oLt?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-06  }}</ref>。隨著哈米甚與海岸線呈平行並沿之移動，當局監視和警報的範圍向南伸展。梅爾維爾角與{{tsl|en|Cape Flattery (Queensland)|弗拉特里角 (昆士蘭州)|弗拉特里角}}之間的警報在3月6日上午取消，同時對弗拉特里角至{{tsl|en|Lucinda, Queensland|露絲達 (昆士蘭州)|露絲達}}之間的地區發出新的氣旋警報<ref name="TCA7">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 7 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f4GQVgWB?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-06  }}</ref>。哈米甚的外圍環流挾帶大雨，導致當局對[[庫克敦|庫克敦]]至[[汤斯维尔|汤斯维尔]]內的地區發出洪水及水浸警報<ref name="TCA8">{{cite web |publisher=Bureau of Meteorology |date=2009-03-06 |accessdate=2009-03-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Advice Number 8 |url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5f4QD5ZYK?url=http://www.geocities.com/dynasmon/Brisbane.html |archivedate=2009-03-06  }}</ref>。

3月7日，時任的昆士蘭州州長{{tsl|en|Anna Bligh|安娜·比利}}緊急簽署防災聲明，允許澳洲官員在受風暴威脅最大的地區撤離居民，確保居民處於最安全的地方<ref name="ABC2">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Nth Qld on high alert as Hamish approaches Cat 5|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510239.htm?section=justin|archive-date=2009-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090310023039/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510239.htm?section=justin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。昆士蘭州政府建議居民採取一切必要行動及作好防風準備，有需要時在短時間內撤離<ref name="BN1">{{cite web|author=Shani Raja|publisher=Bloomberg News|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Australian Resorts in Queensland Threatened by Cyclone Hamish|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601081&sid=avUobnoNh1.Q&refer=australia|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901045202/https://www.bloomberg.com/politics?pid=20601081&sid=avUobnoNh1.Q&refer=australia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而哈米甚直接經過的[[海曼島|海曼島]]沒有進行疏散工作。[[漢密爾頓島|漢密爾頓島]]上的約3000名居民和遊客被當局建議在同日入夜前完成防災<ref name="QN1"/>，島上大部分的船隻被移出水面以免受洶湧海浪侵襲<ref name="ABC3">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Bligh declares disaster situation as Hamish intensifies|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510147.htm|archive-date=2009-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090310000009/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510147.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。小型度假島嶼{{tsl|en|South Molle Island|南莫利島}}和{{tsl|en|Long Island (Whitsunday Islands)|長島 (聖靈群島)|長島}}內的非必要的工作人員和遊客被當局勸喻離開島嶼<ref name="TA1">{{cite news|author=Associated Press|newspaper=The Age|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Menacing cyclone forces island evacuations|url=http://www.theage.com.au/national/menacing-cyclone-forces-island-evacuations-20090307-8ryq.html|archive-date=2009-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090310095137/http://www.theage.com.au/national/menacing-cyclone-forces-island-evacuations-20090307-8ryq.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，撤離至[[弗雷澤島|弗雷澤島]]上較大型的庇護所<ref name="QN1">{{cite web|author=Samantha Healy|publisher=Queensland Newspapers|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Cyclone Hamish could be worse than Cyclone Larry|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25153973-952,00.html|archive-date=2009-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090310161342/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25153973-952,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。州政府宣佈澳洲東北部沿海地區進入緊急狀態<ref name="RN1">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=Radio Netherlands|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=NE Australia bracing for tropical cyclone|url=http://www.radionetherlands.nl/news/international/6205378/NE-Australia-bracing-for-tropical-cyclone|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130502150721/http://www.radionetherlands.nl/news/international/6205378/NE-Australia-bracing-for-tropical-cyclone|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2013-05-02}}</ref>。3月8日，弗雷澤島內估計有1000名遊客開始撤離，同日[[埃利奧特夫人島|埃利奧特夫人島]]及[[赫倫島|赫倫島]]亦相繼有撤離行動<ref name="XN1">{{cite web|author=Xinhua|publisher=China View|date=2009-03-08|accessdate=2009-03-08|title=Fraser island evacuated as cyclone hits Australia|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-03/08/content_10970449.htm|archive-date=2009-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311053529/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-03/08/content_10970449.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。離開[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]和[[凱恩斯_(昆士蘭州)|凱恩斯]]的火車因暴風雨一度被迫取消<ref name="ABC4">{{cite web|author=Cassie White|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2009-03-09|title=Cyclone Hamish hampers rail services|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/09/2511188.htm?section=business|archive-date=2009-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090309211223/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/09/2511188.htm?section=business|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==災害影響==
哈米甚在3月7日為{{tsl|en|Far north Queensland|昆士蘭遠北地區}}一帶引發傾盆大雨，局部地區雨量至少達到300毫米。位於風暴範圍外的[[凱恩斯_(昆士蘭州)|凱恩斯]]雨量達92毫米<ref name="ABC1">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-07|accessdate=2009-03-07|title=Whitsundays expected to bear brunt of Hamish|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510045.htm|archive-date=2009-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090309235959/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/07/2510045.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在昆士蘭州當地時間（[[UTC+10|UTC+10]]）上午10點至下午2點，沿海城市[[麥凱_(昆士蘭州)|麥凱]]錄得148毫米雨量<ref name="QN1"/>，翌日測得136毫米的雨量<ref>{{cite news|author=Sarah Crawford|newspaper=Daily Mercury|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2009-03-13|title=Mackay Hamish warning cancelled|url=http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/09/hamish-warning-cancelled-for-mackay/|archive-date=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312064434/http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/09/hamish-warning-cancelled-for-mackay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。麥凱一帶道路因風暴潮而出現水浸，水深高達6.3米，部分道路被沖毀。據報洪水沒有造成人員傷亡，但有碎片被洪水沖往海裏<ref name="DM1">{{cite news|author=Bianca Clare|newspaper=Daily Mercury|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2009-03-09|title=Hamish's ads height to mackay's king of the tides|url=http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/09/hamish-king-tide/|archive-date=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312050924/http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/09/hamish-king-tide/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據報導，昆士蘭州東南海岸有約二千名居民無電可用<ref name="ABC5">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-10|accessdate=2009-03-10|title=Weakening cyclone Hamish continues to batter southern Qld|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/10/2512309.htm?section=justin|archive-date=2009-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313025522/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/10/2512309.htm?section=justin|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Noosa|努薩}}一名海岸警衛隊成員在附近巡邏時因海浪襲擊而遭受重傷<ref>{{cite web|author=Mike Garry|publisher=Sunshine Coast Daily|date=2009-03-16|accessdate=2009-03-16|title=Coast Guard rocked by Hamish|url=http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/mar/16/coast-guard-rocked-hamish/|archive-date=2009-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319015843/http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/mar/16/coast-guard-rocked-hamish/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Coastal_flooding_from_Cyclone_Hamish_in_Queensland_2009.jpg|thumb]]
{{tsl|en|Yeppoon|耶蓬}}部分地區爆發嚴重洪災，水深高至4.5米，但當局沒有收到嚴重傷亡報告<ref name="TB1">{{cite web|author=Sharyn O'Neill|publisher=The Bulletin|date=2009-03-10|accessdate=2009-03-10|title=Hamish's worst effects offshore|url=http://www.themorningbulletin.com.au/story/2009/03/10/hamish-keeps-his-worst-effects-offshore/|archive-date=2009-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311043918/http://www.themorningbulletin.com.au/story/2009/03/10/hamish-keeps-his-worst-effects-offshore/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[麥凱_(昆士蘭州)|麥凱]]的工作人員花了接近一周的時間清除路上碎片，官方宣佈麥凱的損失總額合共達數萬[[澳元|澳元]]<ref name="DM2">{{cite news|author=Bianca Clare|newspaper=Daily Mercury|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Hamish's hammer blows test marina|url=http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/11/Marina-Hamish-breakwater/|archive-date=2009-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090911160341/http://www.dailymercury.com.au/story/2009/03/11/Marina-Hamish-breakwater/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。位於昆士蘭中南部的國際渡假城市[[陽光海岸_(澳大利亞)|陽光海岸]]海灘遭受嚴重侵蝕，當地有30宗樹木倒塌報告，更有一個碼頭全毀，另一個碼頭半毀<ref name="SCD1">{{cite web|author=Amy Remeikis|publisher=Sunshine Coast Daily|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Hamish hurts Sunshine Coast beaches|url=http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/mar/12/hamish-hurts-sunshine-coast-beaches/|archive-date=2009-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090314043859/http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/mar/12/hamish-hurts-sunshine-coast-beaches/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Bribie Island|布里比島}}被嚴重侵蝕，進一步的侵蝕可能會造成島嶼斷裂，形成一條通往普米斯通的{{tsl|en|Pumicestone Passage|浮石通道}}。黃金海岸進展協會主席米克·格雷厄姆擔心，如果這種情況發生，島嶼和通道的結構可能會改變<ref name="ABC6">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Fears Hamish could submergeBribie's tip|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/11/2512796.htm?site=sunshine|archive-date=2009-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902232416/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/11/2512796.htm?site=sunshine|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在{{tsl|en|Seventeen_Seventy,_Queensland|探索海岸 (昆士蘭州)|探索海岸}}，海灘進一步被侵蝕，大量樹木及部分行人道亦遭海浪沖走，當地官員估計有數百萬噸的碎片被沖往水面<ref name="TO1">{{cite news|author=Rob Black|newspaper=The Observer|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Huge waves wash away sand dunes|url=http://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/story/2009/03/11/huge-waves-wash-away-sand-dunes/|archive-date=2009-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091006142609/http://www.gladstoneobserver.com.au/story/2009/03/11/huge-waves-wash-away-sand-dunes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

3月9日，一艘以[[拖網捕魚|拖網捕魚]]的[[漁船|漁船]]在近[[洛坎普頓|洛坎普頓]]海面上遭[[瘋狗浪|瘋狗浪]]捲走，漁船在被捲走前曾發出求救信號<ref name="漁船"/>。救援團隊試圖尋找三名船員，但受到哈米甚的惡劣天氣而被叫停，延至3月10日恢復搜索<ref name="漁船">{{cite news|author=AAP |newspaper=The Australian |date=2009-03-09 |accessdate=2009-03-09 |title=Fears for trawler crew in cyclone area |url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,25160442-12377,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312075056/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0%2C25197%2C25160442-12377%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-03-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。翌日（漁船被捲走後第三日），當局已找到空救生衣和未展開的救生筏，合理推斷兩名失踪漁民已溺水身亡，並停止搜索工作<ref>{{cite news|author=AAP|newspaper=Brisbane Times|date=2009-03-13|accessdate=2009-03-13|title=Search for fishermen called off|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/search-for-fishermen-called-off/2009/03/12/1236447383137.html|archive-date=2009-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313050739/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/search-for-fishermen-called-off/2009/03/12/1236447383137.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[弗雷澤島|弗雷澤島]]受嚴重侵蝕，岩床暴露在外，導致弗雷澤島北部地區幾乎無法進入。澳洲環境保護局表示，在弗雷澤島退潮期間輕型車輛仍可以繼續沿正常路線行駛，但建議繞行另一條需時兩小時的通道<ref>{{cite web|author=Katerine Spackman|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-16|accessdate=2009-03-16|title=Erosion creates Fraser Is access uncertainty|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/16/2517326.htm|archive-date=2009-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902224020/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/16/2517326.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。哈米甚對沿海岸線內的地區合共造成6000萬澳元（3880萬[[美元|美元]]）的損失<ref>{{cite web|author=Alan Lander|publisher=Sunshine Coast Daily|date=2009-05-07|accessdate=2009-05-08|title=Council to tether waterfront assets|url=http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/may/07/council-tether-waterfront-assets/|archive-date=2009-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090509094439/http://www.thedaily.com.au/news/2009/may/07/council-tether-waterfront-assets/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===大堡礁===
沿昆士蘭海岸線，哈米甚的路徑隨海岸線平行500公里<ref name=":0" />。當時哈米甚的風眼經過[[大堡礁|大堡礁]]大部分區域，成為大堡礁近代有史以來最嚴重的破壞<ref name=":0" />。哈米甚對[[大堡礁|大堡礁]]的破壞更是在過去的二十年中珊瑚礁內珊瑚大量死亡原因之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Extreme Weather and the Great Barrier Reef|url=http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/14308/GBRMPA-ExtremeWeatherAndtheGBR-2010-11.pdf|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=|date=|format=pdf|publisher=Great Barrier Reef Marine Park Authority|pages=10|language=|archive-date=2020-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429023643/http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/__data/assets/pdf_file/0016/14308/GBRMPA-ExtremeWeatherAndtheGBR-2010-11.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多數吹襲大堡礁的氣旋都由東向西移動，並只影響大堡礁的一小部分，相反哈米甚幾乎全程繞越珊瑚礁移動<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Impacts of cyclone Hamish at One Tree Reef: Integrating environmental and benthic habitat data|author=Springer Verlag|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/257377522_Impacts_of_cyclone_Hamish_at_One_Tree_Reef_Integrating_environmental_and_benthic_habitat_data|journal=Marine Biology|issue=159|doi=10.1007/s00227-011-1855-8|others=|year=2011|volume=4|page=|pmid=|access-date=2020-08-31|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901045205/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/257377522_Impacts_of_cyclone_Hamish_at_One_Tree_Reef_Integrating_environmental_and_benthic_habitat_data|dead-url=no}}</ref>。澳洲氣象局估計，大堡礁約有四分之一的地區受到風暴的影響。當哈米甚還是在五級氣旋形態時，部分地區距離哈米甚的風眼在30公里以內<ref>{{Cite web|title=Assessing the damage 2009|url=https://www.aims.gov.au/docs/research/research-highlights/assessing-the-damage-2009.html|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=|date=|format=|publisher=The Australian Institute of Marine Science|language=|archive-date=2020-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419002748/https://www.aims.gov.au/docs/research/research-highlights/assessing-the-damage-2009.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據暴風後對珊瑚礁的調查，珊瑚遭受廣泛破壞，重災區甚至有七成以上珊瑚受損，大堡礁共有一半的珊瑚受損<ref>{{Cite web|title=Storms and cyclones|url=http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/our-work/threats-to-the-reef/climate-change/storms-and-cyclones|accessdate=2020-08-31|author=|date=|format=|publisher=Great Barrier Reef Marine Park Authority|language=|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414220912/http://www.gbrmpa.gov.au/our-work/threats-to-the-reef/climate-change/storms-and-cyclones|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分珊瑚因處於稍有遮擋的地方，幾乎沒有任何損害，其餘幾乎所有裸露的珊瑚都被湍急的水流所破壞。某些地區的珊瑚有活體組織被完全沖毀，只剩下裸露的[[石灰石|石灰石]]。據初步估計，如果沒有任何阻礙生長的因素，珊瑚礁可能需要8至15年的時間才可以完全恢復<ref>{{cite web|author=Sara Trenerry and Wendy Ellery|publisher=In Sciences Organization|date=2009-08-20|accessdate=2010-08-11|title=Research reveals cyclone’s ravages on the Reef|url=http://insciences.org/article.php?article_id=6532|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718113319/http://insciences.org/article.php?article_id=6532|archive-date=2011-07-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

大堡礁內的斯溫斯區一直被認定為珊瑚礁最密集的區域之一，但已幾乎​​被哈米甚完全摧毀。根據研究顯示，因哈米甚的影響，以表面裸露的珊瑚為主一帶幾乎已沒有珊瑚棲息<ref>{{cite web|author=Michelle Jonker|publisher=Australian Institute of Marine Science|date=2009-10-23|accessdate=2010-08-11|title=Report on reefs in the Swains sector of the Great Barrier Reef|url=http://www.aims.gov.au/docs/research/monitoring/reef/ltm200910-10.html|archive-date=2010-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101025164151/http://aims.gov.au/docs/research/monitoring/reef/ltm200910-10.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於珊瑚礁受嚴重破壞，昆士蘭海產工業協會促請當局將大堡礁納入{{tsl|en|Bowen, Queensland|寶雲 (昆士蘭州)|寶雲}}與[[懷德灣_(澳大利亞國會選區)|懷德灣]]之間的災區<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-21|accessdate=2020-08-31|title=Calls for Barrier Reef to be declared disaster area|url=https://www.abc.net.au/news/2009-03-21/calls-for-barrier-reef-to-be-declared-disaster-area/1626088|archive-date=2019-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927035806/https://www.abc.net.au/news/2009-03-21/calls-for-barrier-reef-to-be-declared-disaster-area/1626088|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之前生活在斯溫斯區的魚類在3月25日起不復棲息。大堡礁海洋公園管理局主席拉塞爾·雷切爾德認為，哈米甚對大堡礁造成的破壞，比近代史上任何其他自然災害都要嚴重<ref name=":0">{{cite web|author=Sarah West|publisher=ABC News|date=2009-03-25|accessdate=2010-08-11|title=Cyclone Hamish reef damage 'worst in 30 years'|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/25/2525508.htm|archive-date=2010-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100702085517/http://www.abc.net.au/news/stories/2009/03/25/2525508.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===漏油事件===
{{Main|{{tsl|en|2009 southeast Queensland oil spill|2009年昆士蘭南部漏油事件}}}}
[[File:Queensland_oil_spill_map_small.PNG|thumb]]
一艘載有約60桶[[硝酸銨|硝酸銨]]，長183米的貨船{{tsl|en|MV Pacific Adventurer|太平洋冒險者號}}，由[[新南威爾士州|新南威爾士州]]的[[纽卡斯尔_(新南威尔士州)|新堡]]前往[[印尼|印尼]]途中，經過{{tsl|en|Cape Moreton|莫瑞頓角 (昆士蘭州)|莫瑞頓角}}以東約13公里處時遇上哈米甚的風尾所引起之巨浪<ref name="ES1"/>。該事件發生在一個海洋動物公園附近，該園專為瀕臨滅絕物種提供棲息地<ref name="AFP1">{{cite web |author=Staff Writer |publisher=AFP |date=2009-03-11 |accessdate=2009-03-11 |title=Australian ship spills fertiliser near marine sanctuary |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hDfTijYJZwqeOJVrjYWSomrJrwUQ |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fCenmi5Z?url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hDfTijYJZwqeOJVrjYWSomrJrwUQ |archivedate=2009-03-11  }}</ref>。[[協調世界時|協調世界時]]3月31日約早上8點15分左右，這些裝有硝酸銨的集裝箱與大量重油一起溢入海中，水面因而變得浮滑<ref name="ES1">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=Cable News Network|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Ship spills chemicals in waters off Australia|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/03/11/aus.chemicalspill/|archive-date=2012-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120121083226/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/03/11/aus.chemicalspill/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當局試圖控制漏油程度，但海面波動導致他們無法輕易阻止。有環境保護主義者警告，這些重油可能會對當地野生動物做成重大影響<ref name="UPI1">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=United Press International|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Fuel oil spills from Australian ship|url=http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2009/03/11/Fuel_oil_spills_from_Australian_ship/UPI-66271236770556/|archive-date=2009-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090321163524/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/2009/03/11/Fuel_oil_spills_from_Australian_ship/UPI-66271236770556/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當時貨板上存放着50桶硝酸銨，有31桶墜進海裏<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://newspaperarchive.com/santa-ana-orange-county-register-mar-22-2009-p-36/|title=Earthweek: dairy of the planet (Queensland spill)|author=|date=2009-03-22|work=Santa Ana Orange County Register|publisher=|accessdate=2020-09-02|language=|format=|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903020128/https://newspaperarchive.com/santa-ana-orange-county-register-mar-22-2009-p-36/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成船體破損<ref>{{Cite web|title=漏油事件又一例 澳洲昆士蘭海岸成油污地|url=https://e-info.org.tw/node/41856|accessdate=2020-09-01|author=|date=2009-03-18|format=|publisher=Taiwan Environmental Information Association|language=|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903020130/https://e-info.org.tw/node/41856|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BT2">{{cite news|author=Marissa Calligeros|newspaper=Brisbane Times|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Oil spills from cargo ship into Moreton Bay|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/oil-spills-from-cargo-ship-into-moreton-bay/2009/03/11/1236447253484.html|archive-date=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312001131/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/oil-spills-from-cargo-ship-into-moreton-bay/2009/03/11/1236447253484.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。潛水員檢查船上的洩漏源後發現兩個洞，一個位於水線上方，長10毫米、寬15毫米；第二個則較大，洞口位於船底，約為長一米、寬300毫米<ref>{{cite news|author=AAP|newspaper=The Age|date=2009-03-15|accessdate=2009-03-15|title=Government says it has oil spill under control|url=http://www.theage.com.au/national/government-says-it-has-oil-spill-under-control-20090315-8yq7.html?page=-1|archive-date=2009-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318001901/http://www.theage.com.au/national/government-says-it-has-oil-spill-under-control-20090315-8yq7.html?page=-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

據估計，有620噸[[硝酸銨|硝酸銨]]<ref name="WNA1">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer|publisher=World News Australia|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-11|title=Cyclone oil spill threatens wildlife|url=http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/1011336/Cyclone-Hamish-causes-QLD-oil-spill|archive-date=2009-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904205302/http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/1011336/Cyclone-Hamish-causes-QLD-oil-spill|dead-url=no}}</ref>和250噸燃料從船上洩漏出海面<ref name="BT8">{{cite news|author=Andrew Wight|newspaper=Brisbane Times|date=2009-03-15|accessdate=2009-03-15|title=Clean-up efforts continue|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/cleanup-efforts-continue/2009/03/15/1237054623644.html|archive-date=2009-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319062020/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/cleanup-efforts-continue/2009/03/15/1237054623644.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漏出的燃料最初覆蓋了一個長約5.5公里，寬約500米的區域。雖然硝酸銨對環境無害，但學者指出，高濃度的硝酸銨可能導致該地海洋生物窒息<ref name="AFP1"/>。燃料覆蓋範圍繼續進一步擴大，影響到五個海灘（包括[[陽光海岸_(澳大利亞)|陽光海岸]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://newspaperarchive.com/alamogordo-daily-news-mar-14-2009-p-9/|title=Oil soaks Australian beaches after spill|author=|date=2009-03-14|work=Alamogordo Daily News|publisher=|accessdate=2020-09-02|language=|format=|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903020203/https://newspaperarchive.com/alamogordo-daily-news-mar-14-2009-p-9/|dead-url=no}}</ref>），其他地區的部分海灘被迫關閉<ref name="T1">{{cite news|author=Bonnie Malkin|newspaper=Telegraph|date=2009-03-12|accessdate=2009-03-12|title=Australians rush to clean up oil slick threatening marine life|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/4978493/Australians-rush-to-clean-up-oil-slick-threatening-marine-life.html|archive-date=2009-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090315084116/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/australiaandthepacific/australia/4978493/Australians-rush-to-clean-up-oil-slick-threatening-marine-life.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月13日，洩漏燃料範圍覆蓋約40公里的昆士蘭海岸線，有些地方厚達數厘米。昆士蘭州州長{{tsl|en|Anna Bligh|安娜·比利}}認為由洩漏的覆蓋面和深度顯示船員低估漏油量<ref name="BN2"/><ref name="BT7">{{cite news|author=Christine Kellett|newspaper=Brisbane Times|date=2009-03-13|accessdate=2009-03-13|title=Oil slick puts Moreton Island drinking water at risk|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/oil-slick-threatens-water-supply/2009/03/13/1236447442720.html|archive-date=2009-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416091931/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/oil-slick-threatens-water-supply/2009/03/13/1236447442720.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==後續==
衛生官員及醫護人員希望哈米甚帶來的雨水，可以讓當地的登革熱疫情有所緩和，然而昆士蘭沿海只有很少地區下大雨，從而令疫情持續發展<ref name="BT1">{{cite news|author=Marissa Calligeros|newspaper=Brisbane Times|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2009-03-09|title=Cyclone heightens dengue fears|url=http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/cyclone-heightens-dengue-fears/2009/03/09/1236447102550.html|archive-date=2009-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090312080831/http://www.brisbanetimes.com.au/news/queensland/cyclone-heightens-dengue-fears/2009/03/09/1236447102550.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著天氣在3月10日轉而穩定，救援隊重新開始搜尋三名失踪漁民。在第二次嘗試救援中，發現其中一名漁民生還<ref name="TSMH1"/>。該名漁民獨自一人在昆士蘭{{tsl|en|Yeppoon|耶蓬}}東北約259公里的大浪中被尋回<ref name="TSMH1">{{cite news|author=Georgina Robinson|newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2009-03-10|accessdate=2009-03-10|title=Cyclone Hamish: one fisherman found alive|url=http://www.smh.com.au/national/cyclone-hamish-one-fisherman-found-alive-20090310-8tiz.html|archive-date=2009-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090311024459/http://www.smh.com.au/national/cyclone-hamish-one-fisherman-found-alive-20090310-8tiz.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。救援人員之所以能夠找到該名漁民，全因他打開了原本以為是一根棍子的{{tsl|en|Emergency Position Indicating Radio Beacon|緊急位置指示無線電信標}}。該裝置讓救援人員確定這漁民的位置，不過據說另外兩名漁民並沒有該裝置<ref name="HS2">{{cite news|author=Staff Writer |newspaper=The Herald Sun |date=2009-03-10 |accessdate=2009-03-10 |title=Monster wave saved me from Cyclone Hamish says fisherman |url=http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,25166601-661,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090313043724/http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0%2C21985%2C25166601-661%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-03-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。某團體在3月16日為這兩名失蹤漁民舉行追悼會，沒有開放公眾參與。約有200名認識兩名漁民的人參加此儀式，並在紀念册上簽名<ref>{{cite news|author=Hervey Bay|newspaper=Fraser Coast Chronicle|date=2009-03-16|accessdate=2009-03-17|title=Service honours lost fishermen|url=http://www.themorningbulletin.com.au/story/2009/03/16/service-honours-lost-fishermen/|archive-date=2009-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924040431/http://www.themorningbulletin.com.au/story/2009/03/16/service-honours-lost-fishermen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

漏油事件發生後，昆士蘭州州長{{tsl|en|Anna Bligh|安娜·比利}}宣布兩個島嶼和陽光海岸的部分地區為災區<ref name="BN2">{{cite web|author=Angela Macdonald-Smith|publisher=Bloomberg News|date=2009-03-13|accessdate=2009-03-13|title=Australia’s Queensland Declares Disaster as Oil Coats Beaches|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601080&sid=aZMInXpC.QLU&refer=asia|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901045209/https://www.bloomberg.com/politics?pid=20601080&sid=aZMInXpC.QLU&refer=asia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據報導，由於油污不斷擴散，清理工作每天至少要花費10萬美元，並需要持續一周以上。負責貨船{{tsl|en|MV Pacific Adventurer|太平洋冒險者號}}的總公司[[太古集團|太古集團]]可能面臨150萬美元的罰款。當局目前已派出多支搜索隊前往漏油區，試圖尋找31個集裝箱中可能存在的爆炸物。媒體報導指出，如果[[硝酸銨|硝酸銨]]與[[重油|重油]]混合，可能會點燃硝酸銨，引起大爆炸。如果化學物質沒有與燃料發生反應，但仍然洩漏出海面，海洋生物可能會受到海藻類生物大量繁殖的威脅<ref>{{cite web|author=Staff Writer |publisher=Transport and Logistics News |date=2009-03-12 |accessdate=2009-03-12 |title=Hazardous Cargo Ship Sent Into Savage Storm |url=http://tandlnews.com.au/2009/03/12/article/URKMGGLKSW.html |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318064115/http://tandlnews.com.au/2009/03/12/article/URKMGGLKSW.html |archivedate=2009-03-18 }}</ref>。一隊由88人組成的小組派去協清理油漬，預計再有58人將在隨後幾天內加入<ref name="BT7"/>。在莫爾頓島上，共有290人正在清理油污，其中大部分人集中在{{tsl|en|Middle Creek (New South Wales)|米德爾克里克 (昆士蘭州)|米德爾克里克}}與{{tsl|en|Cape Moreton|莫瑞頓角 (昆士蘭州)|莫瑞頓角}}<ref name="BT8"/>。儘管有數百人在清理洩漏物，但平均每天清理的面積只有一平方公里<ref>{{cite news|author=Connie Levett|newspaper=The Age|date=2009-03-15|accessdate=2009-03-15|title=Oil spill could take a month to clean|url=http://www.theage.com.au/environment/oil-spill-could-take-a-month-to-clean-20090314-8yhd.html?page=2|archive-date=2009-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318213835/http://www.theage.com.au/environment/oil-spill-could-take-a-month-to-clean-20090314-8yhd.html?page=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直到2009年5月，莫爾頓島的油污最終清理完成。清理工作由2,500人進行，合共清除了大約3,000噸受污染的沙泥<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Government of Queensland|date=2009-05-11|accessdate=2010-08-10|title=Moreton Bay oil spill|url=http://www.qld.gov.au/oil-spill/index.html|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100328074145/http://www.qld.gov.au/oil-spill/index.html|archivedate=2010-03-28}}</ref>。

據估計，清理莫爾頓島共花費500萬[[澳大利亚元|澳元]]（320萬[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{cite news|author=Cosima Marriner and Connie Levett|newspaper=The Age|date=2009-03-16|accessdate=2009-03-16|title=Opposition pours oil on flames of ALP election campaign|url=http://www.theage.com.au/national/opposition-pours-oil-on-flames-of-alp-election-campaign-20090315-8yyx.html|archive-date=2009-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090322021847/http://www.theage.com.au/national/opposition-pours-oil-on-flames-of-alp-election-campaign-20090315-8yyx.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就本次漏油事件，太古輪船公司被追加罰款2.486億澳元（1.635億美元）<ref>{{cite web|author=Dennis Passa|publisher=The Scottsman|date=2009-03-14|accessdate=2009-03-14|title='Catastrophe' fear over Australian oil spill|url=http://news.scotsman.com/world/39Catastrophe39-fear-over-Australian-oil.5072019.jp|archive-date=2009-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318015935/http://news.scotsman.com/world/39Catastrophe39-fear-over-Australian-oil.5072019.jp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年7日，太平洋冒險者號船長因在沿海水域棄油而被起訴<ref>{{cite news|author=Australian Associated Press|newspaper=The Australian|date=2010-07-05|accessdate=2010-08-10|title=Skipper faces court over 2009 Queensland oil spill disaster|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/nation/skipper-faces-court-over-2009-queensland-oil-spill-disaster/story-e6frg6nf-1225888017378}}</ref>。鑑於該船在世界範圍內臭名遠播，太古集團作出商業決定，將該貨船由MV Pacific Adventurer改名為MV Pacific Mariner<ref>{{cite news|author=Australian Associated Press|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|date=2009-07-11|accessdate=2010-08-17|title=Cargo ship changes name after Sunshine Coast spill|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/australia/news/article.cfm?l_id=15&objectid=10583724|archive-date=2012-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023153744/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/australia/news/article.cfm?l_id=15&objectid=10583724|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年6月，哈米甚在南太平洋及東南印度洋氣旋命名表中遭{{tsl|en|Tropical cyclone naming#Retirement|風暴命名|除名}}，由赫爾曼（Herman）取代<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Bureau of Meteorology|year=2010|accessdate=2009-08-10|title=Tropical Cyclone Names|url=http://www.bom.gov.au/cyclone/about/names.shtml|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6XP7TIkDS?url=http://www.bom.gov.au/cyclone/about/names.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

